Apraclonidine, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Physostigmine, Acetylcholine, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Brinzolamide, Levobunolol', 'Acetohexamide, Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Rosuvastatin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Miglitol, Albiglutide, Rosiglitazone, Semaglutide, More', 1767369485);
