109757/', '', 'Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Rosuvastatin, Empagliflozin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Miglitol, Albiglutide, Rosiglitazone, Ertugliflozin, More', 'Apraclonidine, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Physostigmine, Acetylcholine, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Brinzolamide, Levobunolol', 1767369485);
