acodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/109758/', '', 'Simvastatin, Guar gum, Rosuvastatin', 'Tinidazole, Tetracycline, Dexlansoprazole, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Esomeprazole, Tinidazole, Tetracycline, Cefepime, Cefuroxime, Secnidazole, More', 1767369485);
